931
01:21:59.980 --> 01:22:07.019
Grygum Pfaff: I feel like I ought to pursue that, but there's no evidence that germs were involved here, so…

932
01:22:07.020 --> 01:22:07.970
Kostadis Roussos: Yeah.

933
01:22:08.850 --> 01:22:13.520
Kostadis Roussos: You're calling it, they're all, they're all victims, right?

