937
01:22:28.110 --> 01:22:28.670
Kostadis Roussos: Alright.

938
01:22:28.890 --> 01:22:29.440
Thorin: Wait, no, this was…

939
01:22:29.440 --> 01:22:30.079
Kostadis Roussos: They agree to…

