01:22:38.780 --> 01:22:41.220
Kostadis Roussos: Chris speaks with Alvin, yes, and then…

942
01:22:41.410 --> 01:22:49.149
Kostadis Roussos: After A'lai did… so A'lai said that he was more likely to be exiled than named Keeper of the Tomes.

943
01:22:50.830 --> 01:22:54.730
Kostadis Roussos: Why was that? That seminar was the…

944
01:22:55.130 --> 01:22:58.000
Kostadis Roussos: I'd have to go dig it up, but a lie…

