Kostadis Roussos: Oh, I gotta… it must be discarded and stopped, that my research, my researchers had so much promise, and skill and value was going to be shut down because people had concerns.

995
01:26:30.690 --> 01:26:33.200
Kostadis Roussos: They didn't see the importance of the work.

996
01:26:35.310 --> 01:26:36.030
Grygum Pfaff: Ugh…

997
01:26:37.520 --> 01:26:42.979
Kostadis Roussos: germ warfare, right? Zalthir, do you want to bring up the book now, or… or not?

