Kostadis Roussos: I then tore the label off the empty poison vial and tied it to the back of the dead winter tree as decoration, and I was burning the vial's label using a candle when Irony and orange glass arrived to lay the table for supper. Irony was carrying a basin of water and decided to wash her… decided to wash his hands.

